&gt; possession.  He shakes his head.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; You go, I must remain here.  Rodimus will need me even though he thinks he
&gt; doesn&#39;t.  The Matrix depends on my actions.  When you reach the Ark, yell
&gt; Leo Prime that I&#39;m all right, and I am trying to recover Rodimus and the
&gt; others who have vanished mysteriously.  Now, to make this look convincing..
&gt; &quot;
&gt;
&gt; He lies down on the ground, appearing to have been stunned by someone.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; When the guards come around and see me like this, they will hopefully
&gt; think that you did this against me and I will act like I have no
&gt; recollection of you doing this.  Part of my neuro circuitry was effected a
&gt; while ago and I still have the scarring to prove it. &quot;
&gt;
&gt; He gives a wink of an eye and puts his head down on the ground, optics
&gt; completely shut.

